abstract: >
  An open-source, sink-guided agentic pipeline for defensive vulnerability
  discovery. Mythos Research Edition is an outside-in replication of the
  scaffold described in Anthropic's April 2026 Mythos Preview (Project
  Glasswing), built around a general-purpose frontier model (Claude Opus 4.7).
  The seven-phase pipeline covers language detection, sink slicing, file
  ranking, agentic hunting, skeptical validation, live-execution (held out of
  the public repository), and aggregation.
